* {{Tlx|Ref improve}} – banner template for when an article needs more than one citation to be added
* {{tlx|Author missing}} – inline template for a specific issue
* {{tlx|Year missing}} – inline template for a specific issue
* {{tlx|Page missing}} – inline template for a specific issue
